Sentencas: Nanostructure cathode material with composition of La0.10Sr0.90Co0.20Zn0.80O5-delta (LSCZO) was synthesized by wet chemical route.
Titulo: Fabrication of high performance low temperature solid oxide fuel cell based on La0.10Sr0.90Co0.20Zn0.80O5-δ cathode

Sentencas: The crystallite size was found 47.55 nm and porosity was observed in the structure.
Titulo: Fabrication of high performance low temperature solid oxide fuel cell based on La0.10Sr0.90Co0.20Zn0.80O5-δ cathode

Sentencas: The oxygen ion and electron transport phenomena were studied from anode to cathode and vice versa by electrical conductivity and electrochemical performance studies.
Titulo: Fabrication of high performance low temperature solid oxide fuel cell based on La0.10Sr0.90Co0.20Zn0.80O5-δ cathode

Sentencas: The conductivity measurements were carried and found 20.29 and 4.87 S/cm(2) in air and hydrogen atmosphere, respectively.
Titulo: Fabrication of high performance low temperature solid oxide fuel cell based on La0.10Sr0.90Co0.20Zn0.80O5-δ cathode

Sentencas: The area specific resistance (ASR) was observed 0.07 Omega/cm(2) at 550 degrees C. Arrhenius plots were drawn to calculate activation energy and found to be 0.09 eV. Excellent performance of 850 mW/cm(2) has been recorded at 550 degrees C. (C) 2018
Titulo: Fabrication of high performance low temperature solid oxide fuel cell based on La0.10Sr0.90Co0.20Zn0.80O5-δ cathode
